---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Travel Experiences | Slow Travel with Pankhuri and Kaushal"
  description="Read about our travel experiences, tips, and stories organized by date."
>
  <main class="py-12 bg-green-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12 text-black">Our Travel Experiences</h1>
      
      <!-- 2025 -->
      <section class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-black border-b border-green-200 pb-2">2025</h2>
        
        <!-- February 2025 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black bg-green-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">February 2025</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
            <!-- Article 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526495124232-a04e1849168c" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Feb 22, 2025
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">5 Must-Visit Hidden Gems in Bali</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Discover secret beaches, temples and waterfalls that most tourists never see on their Bali vacation. Our guide to exploring the real Bali beyond the tourist attractions.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Article 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1575538439014-1b8bc5fcaa1d" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Feb 15, 2025
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">How to Pack for a 3-Week Trip in Just a Carry-on</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Our tried and tested packing strategies that let you travel light without sacrificing comfort. Learn the art of minimalist packing for extended travels.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- January 2025 -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black bg-green-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">January 2025</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
            <!-- Article 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Jan 30, 2025
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">The Ultimate Guide to Street Food Safety</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">How to enjoy delicious local street food without getting sick. Our tips for identifying safe vendors and food handling practices that keep you healthy on your travels.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Article 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526495124232-a04e1849168c" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Jan 20, 2025
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">10 Budget Travel Hacks for Luxury Experiences</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">How to enjoy 5-star experiences on a 3-star budget. From hotel upgrades to fine dining for less, learn our strategies for luxury travel without breaking the bank.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Article 3 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1575538439014-1b8bc5fcaa1d" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Jan 10, 2025
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">Photography Tips for Travelers</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Capture stunning travel memories with just your smartphone. Learn composition techniques, lighting tips, and editing tricks that will elevate your travel photography.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      
      <!-- 2024 -->
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-black border-b border-green-200 pb-2">2024</h2>
        
        <!-- December 2024 -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black bg-green-100 px-4 py-2 rounded-lg inline-block">December 2024</h3>
          
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
            <!-- Article 1 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512453979798-5ea266f8880c" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Dec 28, 2024
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">How We Celebrated Christmas in Japan</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Our unique experience spending the holidays in Tokyo, from traditional KFC Christmas dinner to winter illuminations. Discover the charm of a Japanese Christmas.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Article 2 -->
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md overflow-hidden transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300">
              <div class="aspect-[16/9] bg-green-100 relative">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1526495124232-a04e1849168c" alt="Article thumbnail" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 bg-primary-600 text-white px-3 py-1 m-2 rounded-full text-sm">
                  Dec 15, 2024
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="p-6">
                <h4 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2 text-black">The Best Winter Destinations for Sun Seekers</h4>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 line-clamp-3">Escape the cold with our curated list of warm-weather getaways perfect for winter travel. From Southeast Asia to South America, find your perfect winter sun destination.</p>
                <a href="#" class="text-primary-600 font-medium hover:text-primary-700 inline-flex items-center">
                  Read more
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
